Stripped-down version of the minimal seed. Only packages essential for
a working embedded Linux system.

= Comfortable Unix System =

 * adduser
 * apt
 * apt-utils         # apt-extracttemplates is required for debconf preconfiguration
 * console-setup
 * debconf-i18n
 * kbd
 * less
 * locales
 * lsb-release
 * kmod
 * netbase
 * python3
 * sudo
 * sysvinit-utils    # until "pidof" moves into procps, Debian #810018
 * tzdata
 * ubuntu-keyring    # for authenticated package downloads
 * udev
 * vim-tiny
 * whiptail          # for debconf's Dialog frontend

= Networking =

 * dhcpcd-base
 * iproute2
 * netplan.io
 * iputils-ping
 * netcat-openbsd

= Meta =

 * init
 * ubuntu-minimal
